Is he all right? Do you know?

113
00:13:16,312 --> 00:13:19,281
He's fine-Just fine-

114
00:13:27,956 --> 00:13:31,916
I wish to assure all of Metropolis that this explosion was non-nuclear-

115
00:13:32,094 --> 00:13:33,995
And presents no danger to the community-

116
00:13:34,362 --> 00:13:39,494
- Now, if you'll excuse me- - Hey, what about The Joker, Mr-Luthor?

117
00:13:40,268 --> 00:13:42,430
You heard the man-

118
00:13:45,540 --> 00:13:48,169
What could have possessed me to trust that clown?

119
00:13:50,011 --> 00:13:54,608
Hello, Mr-J-I'm Batman- Eat me, eat me, eat me!

120
00:13:56,585 --> 00:13:59,419
I know you're trying to cheer me up, Harley-

121
00:13:59,654 --> 00:14:02,783
But you see, any time I blow a billion-dollar deal...

122
00:14:02,958 --> 00:14:04,950
