Honestly, Lex, don't you think I feel bad enough already?

124
00:14:29,384 --> 00:14:31,615
You maniac! You idiot!

125
00:14:31,786 --> 00:14:34,485
How dare you use one of my laboratories...

126
00:14:34,497 --> 00:14:35,052
Harley?

127
00:14:37,325 --> 00:14:40,659
- Put him down, baldy- - Mercy-

128
